EWSGI - Eiffel Web Server Gateway Interface
===========================================

This project is a proof-of-concept project for EWSGI. For more details see:

  http://eiffel.seibostudios.se/wiki/EWSGI
  
Required tools
--------------

 1. EiffelStudio 6.8.
 2. Apache (to deploy the example applications).
 
To compile
----------

Compile the two example applications hello_world and hello_streaming_world with
EiffelStudio.

To deploy
---------

Run the script:

$ ./deploy_apache_apps.sh

This will set upp the example applications as CGI programs in /var/www/ewsgi

Make sure to add the following line to your /etc/hosts file:

127.0.0.1       ewsgi.localsite.com